{"tid":2388374,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"買咗機票去加拿大 討論","createTime":"2021-01-31T05:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T10:35:17.000Z","uid":52561,"like":8,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a31c3f52bc9ef60f48291a03c32273733836f75f","tid":2388374,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:33:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bTNk61ak_Mc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbTNk61ak_Mc&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=ffeef910\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bTNk61ak_Mc</a><br />\n<br />\n本身有加藉<br />\n買咗機票二月中諗住去果邊定居生活<br />\n但嚟緊政府會強制旅客落咗地要做多次test<br />\n等結果個三日一定要去酒店隔離<br />\n3日要成2000加幣成皮港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都明政府想少啲non essential travellers <br />\n但真係好唔抵<br />\n有冇人都就嚟飛加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf64734ae78156fe47bd0147ccb9d556896c221","tid":2388374,"uid":221650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:35:38.000Z","msg":"3 日 2000 真係好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401d889ce4f53372849c256e9f1fe595ef72e1d2","tid":2388374,"uid":7050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:40:13.000Z","msg":"我都係，好貴呀屌"},{"pid":"8f1b4f755b5152291af329645a9b0231928d7b64","tid":2388374,"uid":52561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aaf64734ae78156fe47bd0147ccb9d556896c221","tid":2388374,"uid":221650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:35:38.000Z","msg":"3 日 2000 真係好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T05:48:31.000Z","